                                label="Mixed Materials"
                                localtype="box">1</container>
                  </did>
                  <scopecontent id="aspace_8f839e4b81c68904e7ae0da7cb4f03c4">
                     <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                     <p>Dublin Castle <lb/> 2 p.; 24 x 19 cm. <lb/> Congratulates Hopkins on his <lb/> appointment as Master of the Revels <lb/> in Ireland; in the same volume are <lb/> copies of 3 letters from Maddockes to <lb/> Hopkins, dated 1722 Oct 4, <lb/> 1722 Oct 10, and 1722 Oct 13. <lb/> d 1/302 and d 1/304</p>
                  </scopecontent>
               </c>
            </c>
            <c id="ref28" level="subseries">
               <did>
                  <unittitle>KILLIGREW, CHARLES, 1655-1725</unittitle>
