                     <p>London <lb/> 1 p.; 23 x 18 cm. <lb/> Letter solicits order for "The <lb/> History of Richard the Third" by Sir <lb/> George Buc [or Buck] (d. 1623) which <lb/> is to be published by Rees; "now <lb/> first printed entire from the <lb/> original ms. in the possession of <lb/> the editor...Charles Yarnold, Esq." <lb/> is written on a blank leaf of printed <lb/> proposals for this work. <lb/> d 1/143</p>
                  </scopecontent>
               </c>
            </c>
